  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd: \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I am ready to resign: Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has announced that he is ready to resign after securing a majority in Parliament and forming an all-party government.",
        "The Prime Minister's Media Unit informed that the matter was announced in the conference of party leaders held under the chairmanship of the Speaker.",
        "Prime Minister Ranil has said that this decision has been taken because of the resumption of fuel supply nationwide this week, the World Food Program Director visiting the country this week, and the debt sustainability report for the International Monetary Fund."
      ],
